                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18540918-1066-offence-1 t18540918-name-535"></join>Richard Pyle</persName>, the master of Foreman.—2nd <hi rend="smallCaps">COUNT</hi>, charging Florio with receiving the same:</rs>to which</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="185409180139"></xptr>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">FOREMAN</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18540918-1066-verdict-1" type="verdictDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18540918-1066-verdict-1" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
