                  </hi>.Aged 17.—<hi rend="italic">Recommended to mercy.—
<rs id="t18540918-1066-punishment-81" type="punishmentDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18540918-1066-punishment-81" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
